description:
&lt; Made on 48hrs for Mix &amp; Gamejam 2020 &gt;
<p><em>This is what happens when you combine tetris games and a platformer.</em></p>
<p><strong>You will need 2 hands to play this game. </strong>Survive as much as you can on the tetris board while you save your character from being crushed by the falling pieces!</p>
<p><strong>Use a bomb, a drill or even add gravity to the blocks to save yourself!</strong><br/></p>
<p><em>(Author comment: It wasn't part of the rules, but i also limited myself to use only the Pico-8 colour pallete o nthis game.)</em></p>
&lt; Controls &gt;
<strong>Tetris</strong><strong>Platformer</strong>A : Move left<br/>D : Move Right <br/>W : Rotate piece
<br/>S : Drop Piece<br/>Spacebar: Hold piece← : Move left<br/>→ : Move Right<br/>↑ : Jump<br/>↓ : Use item<br/>
<br/>&lt; Some known Bugs &gt;
<ul><li>Drill sometimes don't destroy a block if it hits the corner.</li><li>A bit of lag while using the gravity item.</li><li>"Random" item sometimes (<em>and just happened one time to me but still</em>) doesn't do anything.</li></ul>
&lt; External Credits &gt;
<ul><li>Main song : Chrome Cobra</li><li>CRT Shader : xygthop3</li></ul>
